data.description: Welcome home to a delightful one-level living experience in Brighton. This 3BR, 2BA home offers the convenience of a 2-car garage, neutral colors & spacious great rm w/cozy fireplace that flows seamlessly into the formal dining rm. Eat-in kitchen-gourmet's dream w/subway tile backsplash, pantry & full complement of sleek stainless steel appl. Romantic primary BR w/private double vanity BA. Savor the outdoors in the backyard w/patio. This home is ready to welcome you to the Brighton community.
